s/upload/Image/25(1).png\" width=\"750\" height=\"725\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/26.png\" width=\"751\" height=\"362\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/27.png\" width=\"749\" height=\"249\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/28.png\" width=\"749\" height=\"729\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/29.png\" width=\"750\" height=\"821\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/30.png\" width=\"749\" height=\"691\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\">*1&nbsp;使用Class10或更快的SDXC存储卡来拍摄XAVC&nbsp;S格式的动态影像。以100Mbps或更快速度录制时，请使用UHS-I&nbsp;U3等级或更快的SDXC存储卡。</span><br style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\">*2&nbsp;连拍模式设置为&quot;Hi+&quot;</span><br style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\">*3&nbsp;可使用的自动对焦点数取决于镜头和拍摄模式。</span><br style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\">*4&nbsp;可使用的自动对焦点数取决于镜头和拍摄模式，可选择323个对焦点，不支持动态影像录制。</span><br style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\">*5&nbsp;激活混合相位检测自动对焦点时。在某些拍摄场合，相位检测自动对焦传感器或焦平面相位检测自动对焦传感器可独立使用。</span><br style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\">*6&nbsp;支持的对焦区域取决于使用的拍摄模式和镜头。另外如果选定&quot;连拍：Hi+&quot;模式，当混合相位检测自动对焦有效且光圈设为F9或更高，</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp; 或者混合相位检测自动对焦无效且光圈设为F4或更高时，对焦会在第1个帧固定下来。</span><br style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\">*7&nbsp;蓝牙连接技术可用于以下终端设备（在发布时）：Android（Android&nbsp;5.0或更高版本、Bluetooth&nbsp;4.0或更高版本）iOS（蓝牙4.0或以上）</span><br style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\">*8&nbsp;使用PlayMemories&nbsp;Mobile应用软件。</span><br style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\">*9&nbsp;与手动对焦和自动对焦模式兼容。</span><br style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\">*10&nbsp;仅与手动对焦模式兼容。</span><br style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\">*11&nbsp;使用SAL14TC：与手动对焦和自动对焦模式兼容；使用SAL20TC：仅与手动对焦模式兼容。</span><br style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\">*12&nbsp;智能手机/平板电脑需预装&quot;PlayMemories&nbsp;Mobile&quot;软件。WiFi即时分享功能可能因环境、智能手机/平板电脑的规格或安装软件的限制而失效。</span><br style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\">*13&nbsp;需支持NFC（近场通讯）一触功能的智能手机/平板电脑才能使用，且智能手机/平板电脑必须预装了Android&nbsp;4.0或以上版本的 </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\">操作系统及&quot;PlayMemories?&nbsp;Mobile&quot;3.0或以上版本的应用软件。一触功能可能因环境、智能手机/平板电脑的规格或安装软件的限制而失效。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\">一触遥控只能实现相机的部分拍摄功能，操作时可能会发生画面不流畅的现象。</span></p>', 'images/201707/thumb_img/108_thumb_G_1498955150798.jpg', 'images/201707/goods_img/108_G_1498955150732.jpg', 'images/201707/source_img/108_G_1498955150023.png', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '249', '1498955125', '100', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1', '0', '1499123922', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', null, '0', '0',